PrecisEnactment of the MINORITY INVESTMENT (TRUST AND LOAN COMPANIES) REGULATIONS permitting Trust and Loan Companies to acquire or increase substantial investments in certain bodies corporate, or to divest themselves of shares therein, and imposing conditions on companies that own shares in such bodies corporate.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 1994-0072 Publication Date: 1994-01-26

precis:
Enactment of the MINORITY INVESTMENT (TRUST AND LOAN COMPANIES) REGULATIONS
permitting Trust and Loan Companies to acquire or increase substantial
investments in certain bodies corporate, or to divest themselves of shares
therein, and imposing conditions on companies that own shares in such
bodies corporate.
